    Scope and Contents
Public Affairs Colloquium (PAC) records 1970, consist of brochures on PAC Intersession courses. Series also contains brochures on PAC courses including: "Springfield: It's people and It's Problems," 1974;  "Breaking Barriers to Public Trust," 1974;  "The Constitution: That Delicate Balance," 1984;  and "Contemporary Health Issues, " 1985;  as well as memos regarding PAC planning (1970-72) and PAC curriculum Annual Report AY 1978.  
  
